<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Dogs on Luke Jaeger</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/tags/dogs/</link><description>Recent content in Dogs on Luke Jaeger</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://trickfilm.github.io/tags/dogs/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Trixie Making Pancakes In Space</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/trixie-making-pancakes-in-space/</link><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/trixie-making-pancakes-in-space/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;A highly productive meeting.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Cold Plunge</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/cold-plunge/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/cold-plunge/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Had to wade into the frigid Mill River today to grab Trixie who was stuck in the water — no traction on all that ice! It was only about a foot deep but mighty cold, and of course I fell over a couple of times, so ended up soaked from the waist down. No permanent damage. Fortunately I had a meditative evening at &lt;a href="https://www.jazzshares.org/"&gt;Pioneer Valley Jazz Shares&lt;/a&gt; to process the events.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Still Life With Dogs &amp; Aliens</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/still-life-with-dogs-and-aliens/</link><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/still-life-with-dogs-and-aliens/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Still Life With Dogs &amp; Generator</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/still-life-witih-dogs-and-generator/</link><pubDate>Tue, 24 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/still-life-witih-dogs-and-generator/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Trixie On The Tracks</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/trixie-on-the-tracks/</link><pubDate>Sat, 24 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/trixie-on-the-tracks/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Beast On The Couch</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/beast-on-the-couch/</link><pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/beast-on-the-couch/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Canomorphic Ceramic Pitcher, ca 200-650 CE</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/canomorphic-ceramic-pitcher-ca-200-650-ce/</link><pubDate>Wed, 31 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/canomorphic-ceramic-pitcher-ca-200-650-ce/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href="https://www.atlasobscura.com/places/museo-del-metro-metro-museum"&gt;Museo del Metro&lt;/a&gt; has a lovely display of antiquities excavated during construction of the Mexico City subway, including this pre-Hispanic pup.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Trixie On Rug</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/trixie-on-rug/</link><pubDate>Thu, 13 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/trixie-on-rug/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Another Cross Section Of The Earth</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/another-cross-section-of-the-earth/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Aug 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/another-cross-section-of-the-earth/</guid><description/></item><item><title>The Dog Path In The Waning Days Of Social Media</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/the-dog-path-in-the-waning-days-of-social-media/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 Aug 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/the-dog-path-in-the-waning-days-of-social-media/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Cross Section Of The Earth</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/cross-section-of-the-earth/</link><pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/cross-section-of-the-earth/</guid><description/></item><item><title>All The Round Things</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/all-the-round-things/</link><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/all-the-round-things/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s Higgins Black Magic plus alcohol, in case you&amp;rsquo;re wondering.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Trixie With Powerlines</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/trixie-with-powerlines/</link><pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/trixie-with-powerlines/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Scenic Overlook</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/scenic-overlook/</link><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/scenic-overlook/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dream | Bimble Bamble Bitches (Billy Joel Surgically Disassembled)</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dream-billy-joel-surgically-disassembled/</link><pubDate>Sun, 29 Dec 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dream-billy-joel-surgically-disassembled/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Though he&amp;rsquo;s not in my usual dream lineup, my students had a Billy Joel playlist on the other day and he lodged in my brain. However, I&amp;rsquo;m much more interested in the &amp;ldquo;Bimble Bamble Bitches&amp;rdquo; rap. If anyone cares to record it, I&amp;rsquo;m all ears.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>3 Dogs (If Then Else)</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/if-then-else-final-comp/</link><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/if-then-else-final-comp/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;More fun with anamorphic constructions! I created the illustrations with paper, ink, and Photoshop, and laminated them to ready-made hexagonal painting panels. The custom-built beveled enclosures and the orthographic perspective in the images create the illusion of floating 3D cubes.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
I also love integrating text into images. Words and letterforms are compelling to me because they&amp;rsquo;re both abstract and representational at once. My parents worked in publishing, and yes, I&amp;rsquo;m a bit of a font geek.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
The bathtub image came to me first and it led to the other two. I tried to think of as many examples of &amp;ldquo;things being split 3 ways&amp;rdquo; as I could. Is it the same dog in all three pictures? Maybe, maybe not.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
You can assemble these three little scenes into any number of narratives; pick one that floats your boat.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Underground Creatures</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/underground-creatures/</link><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/underground-creatures/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Drawn during a very lovely &lt;a href="https://www.jazzshares.org/"&gt;Pioneer Valley Jazz Shares&lt;/a&gt; concert at &lt;a href="https://wistariahurst.org/"&gt;Wistariahurst&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Studio Floor Trixie</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/studio-floor-trixie/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/studio-floor-trixie/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Bunny</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/bunny/</link><pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/bunny/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dog Under Manhattan Bridge</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dog-under-manhattan-bridge/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dog-under-manhattan-bridge/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Flying Dogs</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/flying-dogs/</link><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/flying-dogs/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Roller Dogs</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/roller-dogs/</link><pubDate>Mon, 21 Aug 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/roller-dogs/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Everybody Plays The Fool</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/everybody-plays-the-fool/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Mar 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/everybody-plays-the-fool/</guid><description/></item><item><