nk><pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/uninvited-thoughts/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://harpers.org/archive/1993/01/calabasas/"&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m not making this up.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Sasha Reclining</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/sasha-reclining/</link><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/sasha-reclining/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Sasha 2018</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/sasha-2018/</link><pubDate>Mon, 08 Oct 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/sasha-2018/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Triolet For a New American Century</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/triolet-for-a-new-american-century/</link><pubDate>Sat, 28 Apr 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/triolet-for-a-new-american-century/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Created for the Visible Poetry Project, which pairs 30 poets with 30 filmmakers during the month of April. Or anyway they used to. The poem is by &lt;a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/list/1065141.Klipschutz"&gt;klipschutz&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Dream | Hide A Bone, Find A Bone</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dream-hide-a-bone-find-a-bone/</link><pubDate>Sat, 21 Apr 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dream-hide-a-bone-find-a-bone/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dead Dad Dream #3 | Shaving Sasha</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dead-dad-dream-3-shaving-sasha/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dead-dad-dream-3-shaving-sasha/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Fishwife</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/fishwife/</link><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2014 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/fishwife/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;An enigmatic dancing man and a dog-headed woman celebrate the birth of a fish-child, then watch as it takes flight. This bittersweet animated short evokes parenthood’s complex emotional landscape.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Sasha In Alien Landscape</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/sasha-in-alien-landscape/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Feb 2013 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/sasha-in-alien-landscape/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Baby &amp; Dog In Tunnel</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/baby-dog-in-tunnel/</link><pubDate>Fri, 21 Jan 2011 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/baby-dog-in-tunnel/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Dogs Ascending</title><link>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dogs-ascending/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 Jan 2010 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://trickfilm.github.io/art/dogs-ascending/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>